            <p>Distributed across all four scholarship programs yearly.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="impact-card">
            <h3>25+ Student Stories Featured</h3>
            <p>
              Winning submissions published on the OMC platform and social
              media.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="impact-card">
